latestIgtvVideos.title: ITS OKAY TO NOT BE OKAY
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello my fellow earthlings, I know this a little long but a pure heart to heart. Realised how we are all surrounded with so much negativity and emptiness around us. It’s difficult to take it all in at the same time.
I really hope we can make this space a little better. 
SHARE THIS and let’s make the most of this time. We are in this together!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Lag ja gale
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
*Warning- Bear with my voice*
One of my favourite and toughest songs, no one can come close to @lata_mangeshkar ji’s voice ever, so with a heavy heart and a sore throat, this is not for the surr, it’s for the feel and the love of the song. Galati ke liye maafi. 
Kabhi kabhi hum jo mehsoos karte hain usse lafzon mein bayaan nahi kar sakte. 
Kuch aisa hi mehsoos ho raha hai inn dino.
